 	<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="color: #eae46f;"><a href="https://www.behance.net/search?content=projects&amp;sort=appreciations&amp;time=week&amp;search=logo" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span style="color: #eae46f;">Behance, search results for “logo”</span></a></span></li>
